指標名稱Basic Ability Index
本科目對應之指標Correspondent Index
達成該項基本能力之考評方式Methods Of Evaluating This Ability

1具備英語獨立思考判斷知識及應用Be equipped with practical English ability for independent thinking.●》出缺席狀況2具備實用英語口語基本交涉知識及應用Be equipped with basic English negotiation skills in practical situations.&nbsp&nbsp3具備實用英語聽力理解能力Be equipped with good English listening ability in practical applications.●》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)4具備實用英文閱讀解讀能力Be equipped with English reading comprehension ability.&nbsp&nbsp5具備實用英文寫作知識及應用Be equipped with good English writing ability and applications.&nbsp&nbsp6具備英語文翻譯知識及應用Be equipped with good English translation skills.&nbsp&nbsp7具備通過英語檢測之能力Be equipped with the competence to pass English proficiency tests.●》體育測試(含技能測驗、專項體能測驗及體育常識測驗等)8具備跨文化理解與溝通能力Be equipped with cross-cultural literacy and communication skills.●》展演




二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsListening Pro 3, Total Mastery of TOEIC Listening Skills
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online ResourcesTEDGEPTEZtest


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程加強學生之聽力訓練及基本語言測驗技巧 


This course introduces listening strategies to help students familiarize themselves with a variety of spoken discourses, such as English-conducted classes,social interactions, and business meetings. Preparation for standardized tests is also emphasized. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionThis course is developed to help intermediate to upper intermediate learners improve their English communication and listening ability. Quizzes will be given regularly in class and online exercises will be assigned.

